<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.7.9">
<l>kōvā yaivareṉ meykuṭi yēṟik kūṟai cōṟivai tāveṉṟu kumaittup</l>
<l>pōkār nāṉava raippoṟuk kakilēṉ puṉitā puṭkoṭi yāyneṭu mālē</l>
<l>tīvāy nākaṇai yiltuyil vāṉē tirumā lēyiṉic ceyvatoṉ ṟaṟiyēṉ</l>
<l>āvā veṉṟaṭi yēṟkiṟai yiraṅkā yaḻuntūr mēlticai niṉṟavam māṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] five [senses] having taken up residence in my body as masters,</l>
<l rend="indent">badgering me, saying, “Bring food and clothes!”</l>
<l>They won’t leave! I cannot tolerate them! Pure one,</l>
<l rend="indent">you with the bird banner, tall Māl,</l>
<l>You who sleeps on a bed [that is] a serpent spitting fire, Tirumāl,</l>
<l rend="indent">I cannot comprehend doing anything more.</l>
<l>Sighing, “Ah! ah!" pity me, your servant, a little bit,</l>
<l rend="indent">lord who stands at the west side of Aḻuntūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
